&lt;p&gt;At the core of this role is your ability to connect the dots: translating what the federal and regulated market needs into how Tines&#39; platform can meet those needs, and building the narrative, tools, and enablement that bring that story to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own our go-to-market strategy and narrative for regulated industries, with public sector as your primary focus. You will shape how Tines speaks to federal agencies, defense organizations, SLED buyers, and government contractors navigating complex compliance mandates, legacy infrastructure, and mission-critical operational requirements. You will work closely with colleagues across product marketing, public sector, engineering, product, and legal to do that.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to the &lt;strong&gt;Head of Product Marketing&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regulated audiences have unique requirements and demand a very specific kind of storytelling. We need someone who brings the experience to navigate that nuance and is genuinely excited by the challenge of telling a story no one else in the market is telling yet.&lt;/p&gt;
